data.title: Rock Band Setlist Tier List
data.desc: A tier list of every song in Rock Band! Pretty sweet if I do say so myself.
data.author: Colind8

tierdata.name: Foo Fighters - Learn to Fly
tierdata.desc: It's just such an amazing song and it's incredibly fun to play!

tierdata.name: Metallica - Enter Sandman
tierdata.desc: My all-time favorite Metallica song.

tierdata.name: SoundGarden - Black Hole Sun
tierdata.desc: Has the power to put anyone into a chance with its wicked guitar and heavenly singing

tierdata.name: Faith No More - Epic
tierdata.desc: An incredibly fun song with an absolutely beautiful ending

tierdata.name: Coheed and Cambria - Welcome Home
tierdata.desc: You can just FEEL the emotion penetrating your earholes.

tierdata.name: Rush - Tom Sawyer
tierdata.desc: It places you into a trance-like state as you learn the story of Tom Sawyer... I think

tierdata.name: Blue Oyster Cult - (Don't Fear) The Reaper
tierdata.desc: A majestic song with great singing.

tierdata.name: Deep Purple - Highway Star
tierdata.desc: This song is a RIDE!

tierdata.name: Weezer - Say It Ain't So
tierdata.desc: An insanely cool song.

tierdata.name: Radiohead - Creep
tierdata.desc: An incredibly emotional song that really makes you feel something.

tierdata.name: Bang Camaro - Pleasure (Pleasure)
tierdata.desc: It's basically the theme song of Rock Band, obviously it's great.

tierdata.name: Nine Inch Nails - The Hand That Feeds
tierdata.desc: Really cool song with great bass.

tierdata.name: Boston - Foreplay / Long Time
tierdata.desc: This song takes such a long time, but that's okay because it's great either way!

tierdata.name: Bon Jovi - Wanted Dead Or Alive
tierdata.desc: Every time I hear it I think of that fishing show on Discovery...

tierdata.name: Mountain - Mississippi Queen
tierdata.desc: Obviously one of the most iconic Rock Band/Guitar Hero songs. Hot take, but I think the wave group version is better than the actual song don't @ me.

tierdata.name: Black Sabbath - Paranoid
tierdata.desc: I mean, it's paranoid. It rocks. Wavegroup version is worse.

tierdata.name: The Killers - When You Were Young
tierdata.desc: An epic song with great lyrics

tierdata.name: Queens of The Stone Age
tierdata.desc: A cool song with WICKED guitar parts

tierdata.name: Death of the Cool - Can't Let Go
tierdata.desc: Probably the 2nd theme song of Rock Band.

tierdata.name: The Strokes - Reptilia
tierdata.desc: Who doesn't just LOVE this song.

tierdata.name: Crooked X - Nightmare
tierdata.desc: A really cool song. The main riff is really great.

tierdata.name: Anarchy Club - Blood Doll
tierdata.desc: Wicked.

tierdata.name: Red Hot Chili Peppers - Dani California
tierdata.desc: A great song that flows well with epic guitar and bass parts.

tierdata.name: The Sweet - Ballroom Blitz
tierdata.desc: Isn't it funny how multiple songs from this game are on Regular Show?

tierdata.name: Nirvana - In Bloom
tierdata.desc: Probably the best Nirvana song too don't @ me

tierdata.name: The Rolling Stones - Gimme Shelter
tierdata.desc: Epic.

tierdata.name: Flyleaf - I'm So Sick
tierdata.desc: Women, amiright?... Excellent song!

tierdata.name: The Clash - Should I Stay or Should I Go
tierdata.desc: A very fun song!

tierdata.name: Hole - Celebrity Skin
tierdata.desc: Another fun song

tierdata.name: Garbage - I think I'm Paranoid
tierdata.desc: This song has great riffs.

tierdata.name: Tijuana Sweetheart - Seven
tierdata.desc: Another another fun song. It keeps it going the whole song. Fun fact, the band members are employees at Harmonix

tierdata.name: TheWho - Won't Get Fooled Again
tierdata.desc: Has a great intro and the rest of the song is okay.

tierdata.name: David Bowie - Suffragette City
tierdata.desc: Pretty good.

tierdata.name: OK Go - Here It Goes Again
tierdata.desc: These guys make AMAZING music videos

tierdata.name: The Smashing Pumpkins - Cherub Rock
tierdata.desc: A good song.

tierdata.name: Jet - Are You Gonna Be My Girl
tierdata.desc: Probably too low.

tierdata.name: KISS - Detroit Rock City
tierdata.desc: Good song by an okay band

tierdata.name: Iron Maiden - Run to the Hills
tierdata.desc: Cool beginning but the chorus isn't really that good.

tierdata.name: Aerosmith - Train Kept a Rollin'
tierdata.desc: Not the best Aerosmith song...

tierdata.name: Molly Hatchet - Flirtin' with Disaster
tierdata.desc: Cool Guitar parts

tierdata.name: Stone Temple Pilots - Vasoline
tierdata.desc: Probably too low

tierdata.name: R.E.M - Orange Crush
tierdata.desc: An alright song

tierdata.name: Tribe - Outside
tierdata.desc: Cool guitar parts but that's about it.

tierdata.name: The Acro-Bats - Day Late, Dollar Short
tierdata.desc: Not really a fan

tierdata.name: The Police - Next To You
tierdata.desc: Okay.

tierdata.name: The Outlaws - Green Grass & High Tides
tierdata.desc: Why is it so hard aaaaaa. Good guitar parts.

tierdata.name: Honest Bob and the Factory-to-Dealer Incentives - I Get By
tierdata.desc: Some parts are good and some parts are just okay

tierdata.name: The Mother Hips - Time We Had
tierdata.desc: amongus album *cough* kinda a boring song

tierdata.name: The Hives - Main Offender
tierdata.desc: Is he singing or shouting?

tierdata.name: The Ramones - Blitzkrieg Bop
tierdata.desc: The "Hey Ho" parts are cool but the rest of the singing is poopy.

tierdata.name: Beastie Boys - Sabotage
tierdata.desc: Not really a good song for Rock Band and overall a weaker Beastie Boys song.

tierdata.name: The Konks - 29 Fingers
tierdata.desc: An alright song until they start saying "We're the Konks"

tierdata.name: Pixies - Wave of Mutilation
tierdata.desc: Eh

tierdata.name: Fall Out Boy - Dead On Arival
tierdata.desc: Why do they keep including Fall Out Boy songs in Rock Band games?

tierdata.name: Freezepop - Brainpower
tierdata.desc: It's fine, but it shouldn't have been on Rock Band

tierdata.name: The New Pornographers
tierdata.desc: A song that's as good as their name.

tierdata.name: Timmy and The Lords Of The Underworld - Timmy and The Lords Of The Underworld
tierdata.desc: I mean it's a joke song, where'd you expect it to go?

tierdata.name: Yeah Yeah Yeahs - Maps
tierdata.desc: Oh my goddddd its soooo baaaad MAAAHAAAHHAAHAHAHAAPPPZZZZ. It sucks.
